OL,3,CPolice spray anti-social bikers with
OL,4,C'forensic' water to trace them
OL,6,FPolice officers called out to anti-
OL,7,Fsocial behaviour involving motorbikes
OL,8,Fand quad bikes are spraying riders and
OL,9,Ftheir vehicles with a traceable liquid.
OL,11,FThe spray has what Greater Manchester
OL,12,FPolice describe as a "unique forensic
OL,13,Fcode" which can tie potential
OL,14,Foffenders back to a crime scene.
OL,16,FKnown as SmartTag, the sprayed liquid
OL,17,Fglows under ultraviolet light and -
OL,18,Faccording to the force - has already
OL,19,Fled to a number of arrests.
