OL,3,CPolice spray anti-social bikers with
OL,4,C'forensic' water to trace them
OL,6,FSuperintendent John-Paul Ruffle said:
OL,7,F"We have seen 10 arrests made in the
OL,8,Ffirst six weeks of this operation and
OL,9,F54 bikes seized in the process.
OL,11,F"This device will hopefully act as a
OL,12,Fdeterrent to those participating in
OL,13,Fanti-social behaviour on motorbikes, e-
OL,14,Fbikes and quadbikes as they now know
OL,15,Fthat they will be sprayed with a
OL,16,Fsolution that will link them back to
OL,17,Fthe scene of the crime."
