OL,3,CPolice spray anti-social bikers with
OL,4,C'forensic' water to trace them
OL,6,FThose behind the technology point to
OL,7,Fits decades of use deterring theft of
OL,8,Fcash and products in various
OL,9,Findustries, as well as its conviction
OL,10,Frate in court.
OL,12,F"Each canister contains a unique
OL,13,Fforensic solution," said DeterTech
OL,14,FUK's Gary Higgins, "that categorically
OL,15,Flinks offenders and property to the
OL,16,Fscene of a crime.
OL,18,F"SmartWater has a 100 per cent
OL,19,Fconviction rate in contested court
OL,20,Fcases."
